Input Function

Code: variable = input("Prompt message: ")

Explanation: Pauses the program â¸ï¸, displays the prompt, and receives text from the user.

Note: Always returns a String (str) ğŸ§µ. To use it as a number, you must convert it (e.g., int(input(...))) ğŸ”¢.

